<h3 data-string="section.security.title">It begins with total security</h3>
<div class="text" data-string="section.security.description">
The Enjin Crypto Smart Wallet foundation rests on our top-of-the-line security architecture.
It
employs innovative security techniques such as the Enjin Secure Keyboard, rule of two
encryption and other measures to turn your smartphone into a hardware-like secure blockchain
wallet.
</div>
